discussion.content:
1) Yes - Rule `Storage_Access` is allowing access to storage accounts;
2) Yes - Rule `Deny_VM1` is only for Internet Inbound, not for VirtualNetwork, so VM2 can access VM1 via HTTPS;
3) NO - NGS is associated only to Subnet1.

